data.description: Location, location, location!! This beautiful home is located in Sharpsburg, just minutes from I-85, Peachtree City and Newnan. The main level has three bedrooms and two full baths. The fully finished basement is the perfect spot to entertain guests, complete with a bar and a 1/2 bath. The back yard is fenced in and spacious. There is a a separate drive that opens up to a shop in the rear with gravel parking area. Shop is wired with camper hook up and two covered parking areas. Don't miss your chance to make this place your home! Please contact Listing agent for showings, Greg Rainey 770.722.2197. No lockbox on property and need 24 hr notice.
